## Initial conditions: used for the first step
# DOM/BNDY     SIDE           VAR              VAL
.INITIAL 
BOUNDARY       XN               UX            0
BOUNDARY       YN               UY            0
BOUNDARY       YP               UY            0
BOUNDARY       YP               SYY           0
BOUNDARY       ZN               UZ            0
DOMAIN         TEST_FRAME       T             %TEMPERATURE%

